  "text": "Make clean-clone local startup reliable",
  "description": "A new user should be able to clone the repo, run npm install, run npm run dev or npm run start, and get a working local service plus browser UI without manual scavenger hunting. Includes build-mode startup, background service wiring, and sensible port behavior.\n\n**Current state:** Port fallback/reporting is validated and documented. Implementation appears complete but requires end-to-end human verification on a real machine (cannot be tested in sandbox).",
